gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 114, Pacers 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeat the Pacers, 114-109. Nikola Jokic recorded his league leading 13th triple-double of the season, leading the way with 31 points, 13 rebounds and 10 assists, while Jamal Murray added 31 points, eight rebounds and seven assists in the victory. Myles Turner led the Pacers with 22 points and six rebounds in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 31-14 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 24-20.
